long_desc.thetext: Under iOS8 most of the labels are truncated (with ... at the end). Just open http://demo.qooxdoo.org/devel/widgetbrowser/ on iOS8/ipad. This happens cause qx.bom.Label.getTextSize() returns width smaller for 1 px than on desktop browsers.

This should already be fixed. Just check it with a local build and it should be good. But we will update the published devel demos soon so you can also check those latests next saturday.
*** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of bug 8516 ***
